Class Station

java.lang.Object
at.disys.model.Station
public class Station extends Object
This class represents a station central database.
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS station (
id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
db_url VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
lat REAL NOT NULL,
lng REAL NOT NULL
);
